gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Raptors 130, Pacers 122
gameRecap.excerpt: The Raptors defeat the Pacers, 130-122.  RJ Barrett led the way with 24 points and five assists for the Raptors, while Scottie Barnes added 21 points, 12 rebounds, 12 assists and five blocks in the victory. Bennedict Mathurin (34 points, nine rebounds, five assists, five 3PM) and Pascal Siakam (27 points, nine rebounds, six assists) combined for 61 points for the Pacers in the losing effort. The Raptors improve to 22-36 on the season, while the Pacers fall to 33-26.
